singular.cluster.comprised

Class Comprised

  • java.lang.Object
    • singular.cluster.comprised.Comprised

  • public final class Comprised
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Andrew Michel on 10/8/2017. This class accepts an array or list of numbers and determines if any two numbers within the array or list sum into a desired number Comprising is intended to be performed with whole numbers. Caution should be taken when passing a list of floats as the associated method compares generics as longs Based on google interview mock question How to: Work at Google â€” Example Coding/Engineering Interview https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XKu_SEDAykw
